AIM: STUDY AND IMPLEMENTATION OF SINGLE-SIGN-ON.
(https://youtu.be/XbeuDs5WmVM)

STEPS:
1) Go to the below given link,click on try Auth0 for
   free .fill details.
2)Select applications. Click on create application.
3) Select single page web application. next.
4) Download the sample file foe the application 
   which we created.
5)Copy the URL's.
6)Paste it in the application.
7)To check the login type the command.
  ##npm install && npm start
8)It will redirect you to your application you 
  created using single sign on account.
9)This is a sample application for single-sign-on 
  using javascript.
